J4125 PVE x86_64 OpenWrt Configuration

==========================================

1. 目标架构设置 (Target)

==========================================

CONFIG_TARGET_x86=y
CONFIG_TARGET_x86_64=y
CONFIG_TARGET_x86_64_DEVICE_generic=y

生成镜像格式 (PVE 使用 img.gz 或 rootfs.tar.gz 转 LXC)

CONFIG_TARGET_ROOTFS_TARGZ=y
CONFIG_TARGET_ROOTFS_SQUASHFS=y
CONFIG_TARGET_KERNEL_PARTSIZE=128
CONFIG_TARGET_ROOTFS_PARTSIZE=1024

==========================================

2. 硬件驱动支持 (J4125 + AX210)

==========================================

AX210 必须的固件和内核模块

CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-iwlwifi=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_iwlwifi-firmware-ax210=y

蓝牙支持 (AX210自带蓝牙，可选)

CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-bluetooth=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-bluetooth=y

PVE 虚拟机增强支持

CONFIG_PACKAGE_qemu-ga=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-kvm-intel=y

2.5G 网卡常见驱动 (J4125 软路由常见 i225/i226)

CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-igc=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-r8169=y

==========================================

3. 基础必备软件包 (补全)

==========================================

CONFIG_PACKAGE_curl=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_wget-ssl=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_htop=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_nano=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_bash=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_openssh-sftp-server=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_lsblk=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_fdisk=y

IPv6 支持

CONFIG_PACKAGE_ipv6helper=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-proto-ipv6=y

==========================================

4. 用户自定义软件包 (基于您的列表)

==========================================

--- 系统管理 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-argon-config=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-theme-argon=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-filebrowser=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-attendedsysupgrade=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-cpufreq=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-ramfree=y

--- 存储管理 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-diskman=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-partexp=y

自动挂载工具

CONFIG_PACKAGE_mount-utils=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_block-mount=y

--- 网络优化 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-turboacc=y

TurboACC 依赖模块

CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-fast-classifier=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_kmod-shortcut-fe=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-multiwan=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-wol=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-nft-qos=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-sqm=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-watchcat=y

--- DNS 相关 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-adguardhome=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-smartdns=y

--- 防火墙和 VPN ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-firewall=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-upnp=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-wireguard=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_wireguard-tools=y

--- 代理服务 (需配合 feeds.sh 中的源) ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-passwall=y

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-passwall_INCLUDE_Xray=y

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-passwall_INCLUDE_V2ray=y

Passwall2 和 Bypass 可能因源不同名称不同，通常只需保留一个强力的即可

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-openclash=y

--- 容器化 (Docker) ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-docker=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-dockerman=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_docker=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_dockerd=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_docker-compose=y

--- 智能家居 ---

Home Assistant 通常推荐直接跑在 Docker 里，这里是 OpenWrt 原生包

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-homeassistant=y

--- WiFi 管理 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-wifidog=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-wifi-schedule=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-easymesh=y

基础无线工具

CONFIG_PACKAGE_hostapd-common=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_wpa-supplicant=y

--- 监控诊断 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-netdata=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-nlbwmon=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-statistics=y

--- 计划任务 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-scheduled-tasks=y

--- 家庭媒体中心 ---

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-minidlna=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-transmission=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-samba4=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_samba4-server=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-ksmbd=y
CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-ttyd=y

uhttpd 默认已有，显式选上

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-uhttpd=y

--- 其他 ---

移除不需要的包 (示例)

CONFIG_PACKAGE_luci-app-access-control is not set